T1  - Crowdfunding, Financing Constraints, and Real Effects
AU  - Kumar, Praveen
AU  - Langberg, Nisan
AU  - Zvilichovsky, David
Y1  - 2019/10/07
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2020/08/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2019.3368
